title: Affordable Top Corner Apt, Wood Fl, nr U Stone Arch, Trail, downtown
posting_body: ['Affordable top floor corner one-bedroom apartment with great daylight and hard wood floors.', 'Well maintained all-brick building in historic Marcy Holmes residential neighborhood.', 'Features: Big triple windows, hard wood floors in living room and bedroom, AIR-CONDITIONER, window blinds, ceiling fan, and ample closets.', 'Ceramic tile bath, tub with shower.', 'Indoor bike storage.', 'Off-street parking.', 'Updated common areas and on-site laundry.', '(Photos show typical apartment and floor plan.)', 'Convenient location: Short walk to Marcy Holmes Park, Lunds Grocery Store, and St. Anthony Falls shops and restaurants.', 'About 1/2 mile to Stone Arch Bridge and to walking/biking trails along Mississippi.', 'About one-mile walk, bus or bike to U of M, Dinkytown and downtown Minneapolis.', 'Nearby restaurants include Herbivorous Butcher, R Taco, and Brasa.', 'TERMS:', 'Two-person maximum and additional monthly rent for second person.', 'Rent includes one OFF-STREET PARKING space.', 'Rent also includes heat, water, sewer, and household trash.', 'Resident pays monthly electricity.', "Damage deposit equal to one month's rent due at lease signing.", "Full first month's rent due on lease start date.", 'Application fee: $30 per adult.', 'One cat o.k. with payment of pet rent $20 per month.', 'Sorry, dogs are not allowed.', 'When you reply by email, please tell us: 1.', 'how many adults and children?', '2. preferred move-in date?', '3. does anyone smoke?', '4.', 'any animals or pets?', '5.', 'your telephone number and email address.', 'Thank you.']
